sequenceDiagram
    actor User
    participant fe@{ "type": "boundary" } as Frontend
    participant API@{ "type": "control" } as API
    participant db@{ "type": "database" } as Database
    participant ms@{ "type": "control" } as Meilisearch
    participant ps@{ "type": "control" } as PaymentService
    participant pg@{ "type": "boundary" } as Payment Gateway

    Note over User,pg: Phase 1 — Create booking (status = PENDING)

    User->>+fe: Select room + check-in/check-out, click "Book"
    fe->>+API: POST /api/bookings (roomId, checkIn, checkOut)
    API->>API: Auth middleware (JWT + checkBanned)
    API->>API: Validate body (CreateBookingSchema)

    alt Validation failed
        API-->>fe: 400 Bad Request
        fe-->>User: Show validation errors
    else Validation passed
        API->>+db: Find room by id
        db-->>-API: Room or null

        alt Room not found or status != APPROVED
            API-->>fe: 400 / 404
            fe-->>User: "Room not available"
        else Room is APPROVED
            API->>+db: Find overlapping CONFIRMED/PENDING booking
            db-->>-API: Overlapping booking or null

            alt Dates overlap existing booking
                API-->>fe: 400 Bad Request
                fe-->>User: "Room already booked for these dates"
            else Dates free
                API->>API: totalPrice = nights * room.pricePerNight
                API->>+db: Create booking (status=PENDING)
                db-->>-API: Booking
                API->>+ms: upsertBooking(bookingDoc)
                ms-->>-API: Indexed
                API-->>fe: 201 Created (booking)
                fe-->>User: Show payment method options
            end
        end
    end

    Note over User,pg: Phase 2 — Pay (Strategy: Online / Bank Transfer / Cash)

    User->>+fe: Choose payment method
    fe->>+API: POST /api/bookings/:id/pay (method)
    API->>API: Verify booking belongs to user & status=PENDING
    API->>+ps: pay(amount, strategy)

    alt Pay Online
        ps->>+pg: Create checkout session (amount, bookingId)
        pg-->>-ps: checkoutUrl
        ps-->>-API: { checkoutUrl }
        API-->>fe: 200 (checkoutUrl)
        fe->>pg: Redirect to gateway
        User->>pg: Enter card / wallet details
        pg-->>API: Webhook POST /api/payments/webhook (SUCCESS)
        API->>+db: Update booking (paid=true) + payment record
        db-->>-API: Updated
        API->>+ms: upsertBooking
        ms-->>-API: Indexed
        API-->>fe: Confirmed (poll / SSE)
        fe-->>User: "Payment successful — awaiting host approval"

    else Pay via Bank Transfer
        ps->>+db: Create payment record (method=BANK, status=PENDING_REVIEW)
        db-->>-ps: Saved
        ps-->>API: Bank account info
        API-->>fe: 200 (bank details, reference code)
        fe-->>User: Show bank details + upload receipt prompt

    else Pay via Cash
        ps->>+db: Create payment record (method=CASH, status=PAY_ON_ARRIVAL)
        db-->>-ps: Saved
        ps-->>API: OK
        API-->>fe: 200 OK
        fe-->>User: "Pay on arrival — booking awaits host approval"
    end

    Note over API,db: Background — if host does not accept within 24h,<br/>cancelExpiredBookings job sets status = CANCELLED<br/>(and refunds online payments)

    deactivate API
    deactivate fe
